==延伸閲讀==
{{refbegin}}

* {{cite book |author=Parmono Atmadi |title=Some Architectural Design Principles of Temples in Java: A study through the buildings projection on the reliefs of Borobudur temple|publisher=Gajah Mada University Press|year=1988|isbn=979-420-085-9|location=Yogyakarta}}

